title: 1 Marine Killed, Several Others Hurt in Camp Lejeune Training Accident
text:
1 Marine Killed, Several Others Hurt in Camp Lejeune Training Accident   
Sep 03, 2015 DVIDSHUB @ http://bit.ly/1UoREk3 eTN   
One Marine was killed and at least seven others were hurt Wednesday night during a training exercise at Camp Lejeune, base officials confirmed Thursday morning.
